{"tid":28100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］有咩方法可以說服到一個唔撚講道理既老母","createTime":"2016-12-07T17:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T00:59:34.000Z","uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bc7eac28787fc931d1945ca0e0fb31979d8aaa","tid":28100,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:39:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，家母經常起全屋熄曬燈既情況下將手機個mon較到最光，聲稱話較暗少少會睇唔到，我同佢好聲好氣講道理話唔關事，佢唔理我都由鳩佢，<br />\n<br />\n但係近排成日都起好暗既環境無啦啦比佢個mon照一照隻眼勁辛苦，衰啲講句佢盲佢既事，依家晚晚都照到我都忍得幾撚辛苦吓，家母學歷唔高更加唔係啲講道理既人，<br />\n<br />\n到底有咩方法可以說服佢等佢將個mon較返同周圍環境差唔多，叫佢開auto-brightness佢都係唔撚會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d277488f1dd2c2fc4a03c4762e9e8049589d7f95","tid":28100,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"唔小心開錯起吹水台，救吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe5920ece065c41cf26231100db0aa971f49412","tid":28100,"uid":7811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"搵醫學報告同佢講<br />\n事實既野佢無得唔信掛，斷人口"},{"pid":"699b301014a2ba82155e80776add8e73cce24108","tid":28100,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"動之以情"},{"pid":"0e8f92b82d8ca3e48d377e5deac2c79bba16e9ec","tid":28100,"uid":7811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵醫學報告同佢講<br />\n事實既野佢無得唔信掛，斷人口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n斷估"},{"pid":"5260d7c64ad1a13ea554cef903a96bbff786f597","tid":28100,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵醫學報告同佢講<br />\n事實既野佢無得唔信掛，斷人口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢會話你讀到醫先再同我講啦乜乜乜把口咁西利又唔見你讀到書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl